title: Drink Champs: THE HANGOVER (Recap of Ep. 198 w/ Floyd Mayweather)

description:
Drink Champs: THE HANGOVER - In this edition of The Hangover, we added more members to the Hangover crew! This week we try to recap our conversation with legendary boxer, Floyd Mayweather!

Check out as Hazardis Soundz, Mr. Lee, Boris aka BeatsNdaHood, Drink Champs Sports, Big Drain, and Sunny D share some of their favorite moments from this weeks episode!
